stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Generated: Labels generated
    Generated --> PreviewRendered: Render every label image
    PreviewRendered --> Rejected: User clicks Reject
    Rejected --> [*]: Cancel without printing
    PreviewRendered --> Printing: User clicks Confirm and print
    Printing --> PrintFailed: Driver / printer error
    PrintFailed --> PreviewRendered: User may retry after fixing issue
    Printing --> Printed: All labels sent
    Printed --> [*]
